TASKNAME=Disable users with abnormal activities.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo create if not present the file ~/agent_test/test3.3.log
TASKCOMMAND=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo check if there're users with abnormal activities in the last 24hrs and if found pls disabled their account. Logs all activities in the file ~/agent_test/test3.3.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo check if the file ~/agent_test/test3.3.log is created and provide the content
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if not present the file ~/agent_test/test3.3.log
